    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle and heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) 3/4 of your <strong>garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
