    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped basa</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 5 min further or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
